entries.femaleVariant: I've got a sweet new jacket, looking to sell.
Down at the market. I couldn't even look at that old coat of mine anymore, so I swiped it. It's too small, though.
No way. Out in the Badlands, a fancy-ass jacket is like wearing a target on your back. You'd better lose it, quick.
Yeah, well, with that face, anyone can tell you're from here. Nobody's going to target you.
Hah, pretty soon your mom won't even recognize your stupid face.
Relax, I just meant that stunning windswept look you got. You're no blanched, red-eyed corpo from town.
